section_summary: The text appears to be a transcript of a meeting or session involving government officials. The content includes the opening statement by Mr. Issa Al-Kandari, the Deputy Prime Minister and Minister of State for Cabinet Affairs and Minister of State for National Assembly Affairs. He expresses gratitude for the cooperation between the government and the council and discusses the importance of implementing developmental and reform projects according to the constitution. The President also speaks and mentions the approval of certain committees. The text also includes a reference to the legislative session and its topics.
